      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must have documented version control, regression testing suite, and traceable release notes consistent with MRL 2 requirements.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R1 was used under a documented software quality management plan. Version control records, regression test reports, and release notes were reviewed and confirmed to meet MRL 2 SQA requirements. No anomalies were identified in the solver validation suite relevant to rotating machinery or viscous flow applications."
    },
    {
