      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry, which is the same geometry used in the COU. Bovine blood was used in experiments as a surrogate for human blood, consistent with accepted practice. Operating conditions span the full COU range. Minor geometric differences between the nominal validation geometry and the tolerance-variant geometries evaluated in the COU are within the scope of the sensitivity analysis."
    },
