      "acceptanceCriteria": "The turbulence model and hemolysis damage model must be justified for the flow regime and validated against experimental data representative of the COU.",
      "rationale": "The k-omega SST turbulence model was selected based on its documented performance in confined rotating flows and prior validation studies for centrifugal blood pump applications. The Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis power-law model was used with coefficients from Heuser and Opitz (1980), consistent with published practice for MRL 2 CFD hemolysis assessments. Model form uncertainty is bounded by the output comparison results."
    },
