      "rationale": "All model inputs are traceable: pump geometry from FDA-published CAD files, fluid properties from peer-reviewed literature on bovine blood rheology, boundary conditions from experimental test reports. Sensitivity of NIH to ±5% variation in viscosity was assessed and found to produce less than 4% change in predicted NIH, confirming robustness of the model to input uncertainty at MRL 2."
